children.subject: Is 120 any use for ML or generic SWE? Contemplating whether or not to put it on my tentative 4-year schedule.

I can answer for 120, it will take around 7-10 hrs to do the homework, less if you go to OH or have good friends to work with.  Babak is teaching, so it should be very good.  As for utility, it is incredibly useful- signals and systems is ubiquitous in many fields (to name a few: control, dsp, communication, biology, circuits, frankly almost anything physical in the real world :)).
